text (MLText
uid 7777,0
va (VaSet
fg "0,0,32768"
)
xt "-128800,31200,-108800,36200"
st "
This Transition is to enable superceding commands to be sent by the BC. When the BC is busy sending on this bus and another SendMessage is received for this bus, the BC shall interupt the previous actions, provide a tGAP time and then start thenew message.
"
tm "CommentText"
wrapOption 3
visibleHeight 11000
visibleWidth 20000
)
)
